      "body": "From Wouter (https://mailarchive.ietf.org/arch/msg/t2trg/F2m4wb7ZJzB5prAQN4C50Ahz6Ic/): \r\nfor starters current version of specs of OCF is v2.2.2 version 1.0 is a long long time ago.\r\n\r\none can also reference the ISO/IEC version (https://www.iso.org/standard/74239.html ) that is also way better than the v1.0.0 version referenced.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
